# One absolute path per line. Lines starting with # are ignored.
# Re-read every scan cycle (~15s) - no restart needed to add/remove a folder.
#
# Point these at whatever subfolders of your NAS source mount you want
# scanned. Paths must exist and be readable by the musicintake user.
#
# Example:
# /mnt/nas-source/NewMusic
# /mnt/nas-source/ToSort
